809
00:44:33,959 --> 00:44:38,165
You think I don't know
what you're doing?

810
00:44:38,166 --> 00:44:40,499
Split us up, tell him
one thing, tell me another.

811
00:44:40,500 --> 00:44:42,499
I'm a cop,
you fucking moron.

812
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:44,916
It was interesting

813
00:44:44,917 --> 00:44:49,166
because I couldn't
find the words to express...

814
00:44:53,667 --> 00:44:58,458
...to express the dismay I feel
at what I saw outside...

815
00:44:59,542 --> 00:45:02,332
Hundred people,
ordinary decent citizens,

816
00:45:02,333 --> 00:45:05,708
