an occupying army.

818
00:45:09,166 --> 00:45:11,249
Aren't they?

819
00:45:11,250 --> 00:45:13,458
You know where
I've seen this before?

820
00:45:15,208 --> 00:45:19,374
Some of the most fucked-up
places on the planet,

821
00:45:19,375 --> 00:45:21,083
