we're not...

822
00:45:23,041 --> 00:45:26,374
Iraq, Afghanistan, Syria.

823
00:45:26,375 --> 00:45:31,792
Locals facing the armies
of governments they hate.

824
00:45:34,250 --> 00:45:38,207
All it takes is one wrong word,
one wrong move,

825
00:45:38,208 --> 00:45:41,165
and people start dying.

826
00:45:41,166 --> 00:45:44,207
Get the Feds to leave,
the folks will go home.

827
00:45:44,208 --> 00:45:46,791
The FBI won't leave
without O'Keefe.

828
00:45:46,792 --> 00:45:49,040
Then you got a problem.

829
00:45:49,041 --> 00:45:50,624
No, you got a problem.
That's what I'm saying.

830
00:45:50,625 --> 00:45:54,249
These are your people,
people you swore to protect.

831
00:45:54,250 --> 00:45:56,709
You're leaving them out there
in harm's way.

832
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:04,291
I know Brett O'Keefe.
He knows me.

833
00:46:05,542 --> 00:46:06,917
Tell me where you took him.

834
00:46:09,959 --> 00:46:13,666
I'll go talk to him.

835
00:46:13,667 --> 00:46:15,083
Alone.

836
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,582
I will end this.

837
00:46:18,583 --> 00:46:22,416
No one will get hurt.

838
00:46:22,417 --> 00:46:24,000
You have my word.

839
